              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Direct cross section measurement."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The photodisintegration  of  235U  has  been studied,",
                " using nearly monochromatic photons obtained from the",
                " annihilation in   flight   of  fast  positrons.  The",
                " partial cross sections sigma(g,F), sigma(g,n),",
                " and sigma(gamma,2n) were determined. Integrated cross",
                " sections for these reactions were found to be  1.07,",
                " 1.00, and 1.49 MeV*b, respectively. Structure in the",
                " giant resonance  of  the  compound-nucleus-formation",
                " cross section   was   observed   and   from  this  a",
                " quadrupole moment of 12.8 (1.3)b  was  found.  An",
                " energy dependence in  the  quantity  width-n/width-F",
                " was observed."
              ]
            }
          ],
